				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It's a decay, linear (saw) in amplitude space but quantized to 16 levels, from maximum amplitude to silence. The time of the decay can be controlled between 1/15 and 16/15 seconds in 1/15 second units. Whether or not the volume resets to maximum after expiring can also be controlled.<br /><br />Very few games past 1983-1984 actually used the envelope outside constant volume mode.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
